snippet.title: House of Memories - Announcement Trailer
snippet.description:
The Raincoat Man is a third person horror game. Through the years the legend of the raincoat man haunted the Rocksfield City and now he is back to catch you. Be aware, he is always looking for you.

Wishlist and play NOW on STEAM:
https://store.steampowered.com/app/1935620/House_of_Memories/

FOLLOW THE SOCIAL MEDIAS:
Twitter: https://twitter.com/GundesGames
Instagram: https://www.instagram.com/GundesGames/
Facebook: https://www.facebook.com/GundesGames

Hashtag: #HouseOfMemories #HorrorGame
